TALK Narrator The shield will protect you from most enemy attacks
TALK Narrator Some enemy attacks, most notably those from bosses, cannot be blocked
TALK Narrator Environmental hazards, such as falling rocks, cannot be blocked
TALK Narrator To block an attack, press and hold block (left alt).
TALK Narrator You must be facing the attack to succesfully block it
TALK Narrator Note that you cannot move whilst blocking, but you can face the other way. You also cannot block in the air
TALK Narrator Pick up the shield and continue to the right
